            "body": "Hi @gouyang\n\nI am closing this as this is not an issue with `buildah`.\nRunning `buildah inspect -h` does specify the order of the argument and so as @rhatdan explained the `-f` option should be before the `IMAGE` or the `CONTAINER` argument:\n\n```\nUSAGE:\n   buildah inspect [command options] CONTAINER-OR-IMAGE\n```\n\nThank you so much for reporting this. "
